<br />
If it does not connect, it may still be the credentials, you will want to reset the password for the database user and try again.<br />
<br />
It is also a slight possibility the MySQL service was interrupted on the server. If you believe that is the case, you will want to <a href="http://www.inmotionhosting.com/support/website/website-troubleshooting/how-to-get-great-technical-support">contact our Live Support department</a> and they can check your individual server for you.<br />
<br />
